        </p>

        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>How do I book a seat?</strong> <br> Navigate to the booking page, select your route, choose your preferred bus, and pick an available seat. Confirm the booking to complete the process.</li>
            <li><strong>Can I cancel my reservation?</strong> <br> Yes, cancellations can be made up to 24 hours before the scheduled departure time. Get in contact with us to cancel your booking.</li>
            <li><strong>What payment methods do you accept?</strong> <br> We accept M-Pesa, credit/debit cards, and other mobile money services.</li>
        </ul>

